title: Volleyball Roundup: Wynford beats Bucyrus
text:
Volleyball Roundup: Wynford beats Bucyrus Telegraph-Forum staff report 9:29 p.m. EDT October 15, 2015 CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Buckeye Central 3, Mohawk 0 
Buckeye Central swept Mohawk (25-12, 25-18, 25-16) on Thursday. Jenna Delarber had 11 kills and three blocks, Jenna Karl had 10 kills, two aces, and 14 digs; and Sarah Heydinger had eight kills and four aces. Bailey Agin Had 11 digs and five aces, Addie Ackerman had 27 assists and six digs and Erin Baldosser had five digs and three aces. 
Wynford 3, Bucyrus 0 
Wynford swept Bucyrus (25-16, 25-14, 25-15) in Northern 10 Athletic Conference play on Thursday. Maci Cooper had eight kills, Tara Zinser had nine kills and three blocks, Alyssa Harrer had five aces and three blocks, Mallory Moore had 11 digs, Jade Stukman had 12 digs and Rhieannae Cory had 22 assists and 12 digs for the Royals.
